{
  "stem": "19895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 250.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it's pretty easy to understand the name Grunwald-- who was our teacher in Hungarian language and German language and was the so-called class master on-- of, of our first six years of our gymnasium life.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the other hand, he probably-- very honestly-- he probably overemphasized his love and his, his admiration for German culture, which at the time we didn't understand the same way as he wanted to deliver it in a truly literary and educational standpoint.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and we were somewhat disappointed, even in the school's approach during those terrible years of the Holocaust and the years leading up to it, that we were, in some degree, were like lambs.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't teach us to stand up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what I mean by that, that we just had to follow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they seen it as a part of surviving just to go along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were not, at age 16, try to resist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just lambs who had to follow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to end the story about teachers, when we came back to school after the war ended-- and those of us who survived, which was a very painful decision-- but we asked Jeno Grunwald [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to quit.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SOB] And we chose Strasser to be our guna-- class master.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm choking up when I say that because I still liked him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I came to the United States, I sent an invitation to him for my wedding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I got married in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And at the hotel where the wedding took place, at the Gotham Hotel, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the rabbi who officiated there was the same rabbi who officiated the wedding ceremonies for my in-laws, my wife's parents.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
